# GRAPHICS::SET_DISTANCE_BLUR_STRENGTH_OVERRIDE

## Summary
Overrides strength of distance blur (i.e. simple DOF) for a frame (keep calling every frame you wish to override the strength)

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** param
